      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Burma Pond (Secesh Reservoir)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7DkYkVfSQZRDJqtg2mwhvzX3KcxyVY6tZ00CNp5alNTm7SWLBDzZHiv-F_49ncEBbKQfHZiXz3zvEGxlQBSw_s8z-UW87UNF564mS0FHt8crBNvRV04ApP25YKZ27fgyqOsOj-m_tEWS1YlWoYTw" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is a 4.5-acre pond located approximately 8 miles from the community of Wolf Creek in Josephine County, Oregon. There is easy access along the bank side of this pond. Only non-motorized boats are allowed. Due to the steepness of BLM Road #33-5-15.2, the last half mile to the site, four-wheel-drive is recommended.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout, largemouth bass, bluegill<br> <br><br> <br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/southwest-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v7DkYkVfSQZRDJqtg2mwhvzX3KcxyVY6tZ00CNp5alNTm7SWLBDzZHiv-F_49ncEBbKQfHZiXz3zvEGxlQBSw_s8z-UW87UNF564mS0FHt8crBNvRV04ApP25YKZ27fgyqOsOj-m_tEWS1YlWoYTw</value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            -123.274101,42.703973,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Butterfield Lake</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6UtcrbPYI70Rt_mZj4xJfNSYMAX-GTEqDW7AXdiGwWJbV5UurV8rX2vnIMzslcsL9s-aM_cZ0jjF4FRhr54ImBLTjAscUPBfLg_n6Smh1wa8CCTmWNdyphgtUxgznvpUsGeuEO1yMgoc4OSKFFtMnPM_Ar-gs" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This 50-acre lake is located about six miles north of Coos Bay, and just west of Highway 101 in the Riley Ranch Campground (http://www.co.coos.or.us/Departments/CoosCountyParks/RileyRanch.aspx) operated by Coos County Parks (http://www.co.coos.or.us/Departments/CoosCountyParks.aspx). An access road from the campground to the lake allows trout stocking trucks to reach the lake, and provides access for anglers to launch small “cartop” boats and canoes. Fishing docks also provide angler access. <br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, largemouth bass, bluegill, warmouth<br><br> <br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/southwest-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6UtcrbPYI70Rt_mZj4xJfNSYMAX-GTEqDW7AXdiGwWJbV5UurV8rX2vnIMzslcsL9s-aM_cZ0jjF4FRhr54ImBLTjAscUPBfLg_n6Smh1wa8CCTmWNdyphgtUxgznvpUsGeuEO1yMgoc4OSKFFtMnPM_Ar-gs</value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            -124.219505,43.519054,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Dutch Herman Pond</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6cK9WDTt5XEk2VjOh5SLDn4AsKtGw7Z1FKQ0XpLPlx62TB3o3OrzeAKYAT-VHoI8TYYwLw_heE_hRIV6dO3f_h1A-kg-picYOfwubxAbD4j_imIN2BVOsjvUIeqE8QMlp4xMUj6DkcGtZRlx3iuG4GQ_bGZyFi" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is a 2-acre pond east of the community of Wolf Creek.<br><br>Fish species: rainbow trout, bass, bluegill<br><br><br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/southwest-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v6cK9WDTt5XEk2VjOh5SLDn4AsKtGw7Z1FKQ0XpLPlx62TB3o3OrzeAKYAT-VHoI8TYYwLw_heE_hRIV6dO3f_h1A-kg-picYOfwubxAbD4j_imIN2BVOsjvUIeqE8QMlp4xMUj6DkcGtZRlx3iuG4GQ_bGZyFi</value>
          </Data>
