      <Placemark>
        <name>Little Hyatt Reservoir</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Species Stocked: rainbow trout<br><br>Description: 7.5 acre surface area reservoir. North part of the reservoir is private property, south part is BLM.<br><br>Amenities: Primitive site, suitable for personal pontoon boat, or bank fishing. <br><br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/southwest-zone/)<br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br><br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
