      <Placemark>
        <name>Lost Creek Reservoir</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5Eje4ZzNkFkzJqBK0d_LVQtcRorjTviFdygxLveX5lx32v-v0oVVFxF5WGRQkZd2Lywi62qQalj0-6e-sS4xR9-FcGeWa1bi7b0gld03RNNAYzMOWWwH1KO8kbf4oWAy2McCDoQ04pGeD6FugWQbVsyYeYtWOsD1a-" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is a 3,500-acre impoundment on the Rogue River above Shady Cove, Ore. It is deep throughout, reaching a maximum depth of 322 feet. Camping and a boat ramp is available at Stewart State Park (http://www.oregonstateparks.org/park_30.php) on the south shore. A second boat ramp is located next to the dam on the north end of the lake.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout, cutthroat trout, brown trout, spring chinook, largemouth bass, smallmouth bass, bluegill, crappie, pumpkinseed sunfish, brown bullhead<br> <br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/southwest-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-53</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5Eje4ZzNkFkzJqBK0d_LVQtcRorjTviFdygxLveX5lx32v-v0oVVFxF5WGRQkZd2Lywi62qQalj0-6e-sS4xR9-FcGeWa1bi7b0gld03RNNAYzMOWWwH1KO8kbf4oWAy2McCDoQ04pGeD6FugWQbVsyYeYtWOsD1a-</value>
