        <name>Weaver pond</name>
        <description><![CDATA[ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/southwest-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (https://myodfw.com/fishing/species/trout/stocking-schedule)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
