      <Placemark>
        <name>Clearwater Number Two Forebay - Umpqua</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v5X_FGiUQSSL4eUPUcyoVxKf6oLFYPyVrSPaRbiv3sZAa2EL_MVOg8tZrBY7yX3vcdINWSiq0ne_Q3xPQpfDLa7m0FN8-8PEVtSwf8Bc6Y2zVwmIXmyz5ChIKXaAkDHkpd60ZSlETSKTkJoNApxL1FtE_vWMIHLY0Q" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This is one of two forebays in the area and is the only one that is part of ODFW's trout stocking program.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br> <br><br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/southwest-zone/)<br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
