      <Placemark>
        <name>Connie Lake - Umpqua</name>
        <description><![CDATA[This is a small lake in the Umpqua National Forest (http://www.fs.usda.gov/umpqua) that is accessible by 4-wheel-drive.  The lake is annually stocked with fingerling Rainbow Trout.<br><br>Fish species: brook trout, Rainbow Trout<br> <br><br>ODFW Recreation Report & regulation updates (http://myodfw.com/recreation-report/fishing-report/southwest-zone/)<br><br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.eregulations.com/oregon/fishing/)]]></description>
